Content:: Matthew James Keeling OBE (born June 1970) is a professor in the Mathematics Institute and the School of Life Sciences of the University of Warwick. He has been editor of the journal Epidemics since 2007.[1][2] Keeling was appointed Officer of the Order of the British Empire (OBE) in the 2021 Birthday Honours for services to SAGE during the Covid-19 response.[3]  This biography article of a United Kingdom academic is a stub.
